short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Update aws dark mode cookie on page load

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Amazon AWS has begun the infrastructure to enable a dark mode on select web pages in their console via a cookie. This extension will set and attempt to keep the cookie in dark mode.
